---
---

<section class="p-products" id="products">
  <div class="u-section">
    <div class="p-products__header js-fade-up">
      <p class="p-products__label">PRODUCTS</p>
      <h2 class="p-products__title">商品紹介</h2>
      <p class="p-products__lead">その時期、最も美味しい品種をお届けします。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-products__grid">
      <!-- Shine Muscat -->
      <div class="p-products__card js-fade-up">
        <div class="p-products__card-img">
          <img src="/images/shine-muscat.webp" alt="シャインマスカット" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-products__card-body">
          <span class="p-products__card-season">9月上旬〜</span>
          <h3 class="p-products__card-name">シャインマスカット</h3>
          <p class="p-products__card-desc">大粒で種がなく、皮ごと食べられる贅沢なぶどう。パリッとした食感と上品な甘さが特徴です。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sun Fuji -->
      <div class="p-products__card js-fade-up">
        <div class="p-products__card-img">
          <img src="/images/sun-fuji.webp" alt="サンふじ" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-products__card-body">
          <span class="p-products__card-season">11月中旬〜</span>
          <h3 class="p-products__card-name">サンふじ</h3>
          <p class="p-products__card-desc">リンゴの王様。太陽の光をたっぷり浴びて育ち、蜜入りが良く、芳醇な香りと濃厚な甘みが特徴。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Shinano Sweet -->
      <div class="p-products__card js-fade-up">
        <div class="p-products__card-img">
          <img src="/images/shinano-sweet.webp" alt="シナノスイート" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-products__card-body">
          <span class="p-products__card-season">10月上旬〜</span>
          <h3 class="p-products__card-name">シナノスイート</h3>
          <p class="p-products__card-desc">酸味が少なく濃厚な甘み。「ふじ」と「つがる」の交配種で、果汁が多くシャキッとした食感が人気。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Kyoho -->
      <div class="p-products__card js-fade-up">
        <div class="p-products__card-img">
          <img src="/images/kyoho.webp" alt="巨峰" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="p-products__card-body">
          <span class="p-products__card-season">9月下旬〜</span>
          <h3 class="p-products__card-name">巨峰</h3>
          <p class="p-products__card-desc">ぶどうの王様。濃厚な甘みと芳醇な香りが口いっぱいに広がる、日本を代表する品種。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
